<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Destinations</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: white;
        }

        header {
            background-color: rgb(31, 24, 225);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: rgb(31, 24, 225);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0 1rem;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* nav ul li a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        } */

        h1,
        h2,
        h3 {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: #333;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .destination {
            background: #222;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .destination:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .destination h3 {
            color: white;
        }

        .destination p {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            color: rgb(116, 111, 111);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            background: rgb(37, 10, 215);
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .hr {
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Explore Our Destinations</h1>
        <p>Discover amazing places around the world.</p>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/home" class="no-underline hover:no-underline">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="no-underline hover:no-underline">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/destination" class="no-underline hover:no-underline">Destinations</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="no-underline hover:no-underline">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <div id="destinations" class="container">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Ujjain</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Mahakaleshwar Temple, Kal Bhairav Temple, Ram Ghat</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> October to March</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> A spiritual hub with ancient temples and serene ghats.</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Goa</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Beaches, Fort Aguada, Basilica of Bom Jesus</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> November to February</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> Relaxing beaches, vibrant nightlife, and Portuguese heritage.</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Maldives</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Overwater Villas, Coral Reefs, Male City</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> November to April</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> Pristine beaches, luxury resorts, and underwater adventures.</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Agra</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Taj Mahal, Agra Fort, Fatehpur Sikri</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> November to March</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> Iconic Mughal architecture and cultural history.</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Varanasi</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Ganga Aarti, Kashi Vishwanath Temple, Sarnath</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> October to March</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> Spiritual experiences and ancient ghats.</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Kashmir</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Dal Lake, Gulmarg, Pahalgam</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> March to August</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> Scenic beauty, houseboats, and adventure activities.</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Shimla</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Mall Road, Kufri, Jakhoo Temple</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> March to June</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> Pleasant weather, colonial charm, and snowy peaks.</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="hr">
        <div class="destination">
            <h3>Badrinath</h3>
            <p><strong>Highlights:</strong> Badrinath Temple, Mana Village, Vasudhara Falls</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> May to October</p>
            <p><strong>Why Visit:</strong> Sacred pilgrimage site and stunning Himalayan views.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Travel Planner. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>